                            <comment id="17579166" author="dcapwell" created="Fri, 12 Aug 2022 22:29:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 from me, but before merge we need to confirm the 4.0 version&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17584644" author="krummas" created="Thu, 25 Aug 2022 06:21:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;tests look fine, I&apos;ll get this committed once 4.0.6 has been released (so we can set the correct 4.0 since version (4.0.7-SNAPSHOT) without breaking the tests)&lt;/p&gt;

